### Create a new university
POST http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/universities/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample University",
  "country_id": 1,
  "country_name": "Sample Country",
  "ranking": 1,
  "student_count": 25000,
  "established_year": 2000,
  "type": "Public",
  "website": "https://sampleuniversity.edu",
  "courses": "Engineering, Science, Arts",
  "address": "123 Sample Street, Sample City",
  "description": "A sample university for testing purposes.",
  "unique_feature": "Sample unique feature",
  "average_tuition": 12000.00
}


### Get all universities for a specific country
GET http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/universities/
Accept: application/json

### Update an existing university
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/universities/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated University",
  "ranking": 1,
  "studentCount": 50000,
  "establishedYear": 1900,
  "type": "Public",
  "website": "https://updated-university.edu",
  "courses": "Engineering, Arts",
  "address": "Updated Address",
  "description": "Updated description"
}
